{"tid":489522,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)律政英雄2HERO2","createTime":"2017-12-04T17:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T13:12:52.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e15d5e090c65c37a950173f2a739cde7766fcd","tid":489522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=12e1f47a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=84deb9e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e9e5a27e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/37/HERO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F37%2FHERO2.jpg&h=baefeff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睽違13年，HERO回來了！久利生公平（木村拓哉飾）檢察官帥氣再現，與正妹事務官北川景子全新搭檔，鍥而不捨揭發所有事件的真相！富士電視台傾全力重金打造，萬眾矚目經典日劇，今年暑假全亞洲就瘋這一部！<br />\n東京地檢城西支部的成員，都在八卦新檢察官報到的消息。而即將與新任檢察官搭檔的，是看似大小姐卻會撂狠話的事務官麻木千佳（北川景子飾）。某日千佳走進辦公室，竟發現有個男人一身休閒牛仔褲，正在如火如荼的健身？！他，就是傳說中的檢察官久利生公平（木村拓哉飾）！<br />\n久利生才剛到任，便立刻展開偵訊。嫌犯大西（森山直太朗飾）的指紋和15年前的寶石大盜一模一樣，但大西卻矢口否認。眼見強盜案時效即將在3天後到期，久利生要如何在各方壓力下，找出事件的真相？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f730b976\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4109c3cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7f9d946758791a203203c89d3af62038c1af8e","tid":489522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e4b85631597903a7be358e760ce09f901e19ef","tid":489522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T18:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7afac6db586dea678ac9b6c28e37f9b34b09e","tid":489522,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T19:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb284aa036afcfc7184e9620a7b0b776